title: Two Guys Smoke Shop 27th Anniversary Party
itunes:title: Two Guys Smoke Shop 27th Anniversary Party
description: We're live on the scene for Two Guys Smoke Shop 27th Anniversary Party! Join us as we interview cigarlebrities including Jorge Padron from Padron Cigars, Steve Saka from Drew Estates, Nick Perdomo for Perdomo Cigars,  Jim Young from Davidoff, Eric Hanson from Hammer and Sickle, Eric Newman from JC Newman, Rocky Patel from Rocky Patel Premium Cigars, Jerry from Ben & Jerry's Ice Cream, Ernesto Perez-Carrillo from EP Carrillo Cigars, Victor Vitale from The Cigar Agency, and many more stars from inside the cigar world.
